66
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:29,670
Yun.

67
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:31,720
Why don't you buy this unit?

68
00:03:32,670 --> 00:03:33,800
I'm not buying it.

69
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,000
-Why not?
-Why not?

70
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,880
