81
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,030
Sure.

82
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,080
I'll get going.

83
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,670
Sure.

84
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,550
Take care.

85
00:04:07,550 --> 00:04:08,080
Bye, Yun.

86
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:13,880
What was that for?

87
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,830
You know what?

88
