Mr. Wang,

172
00:07:53,230 --> 00:07:55,390
we can negotiate the cost.

173
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,110
Hey.

174
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:10,600
You've worked hard.

175
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,040
Let's grab some coffee. My treat.

176
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,390
Sure.

177
