♪You are a part of my story♪

188
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:03,800
♪I want to use my heartbeat to exchange with you♪

189
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:04,880
♪This second♪

190
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:08,580
